0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:59:45.000Z","msg":"暗黑兵法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:02:10.000Z","msg":"淋病獻頭"},{"pid":"4ca921230d713e9a0ff23e6835c279e0671c5510","tid":1217000,"uid":54337,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"古有齊威王、越王勾踐、德川家康。<br />\n今有淋病月娥。<br />\n<br />\n平時庸碌無能，廢閪到核爆。<br />\n不飛則已，飛則一飛沖天。<br />\n不鳴則已，鳴則一鳴驚人。<br />\n<br />\n點估到一個師奶，連八達通都唔識用，廁紙都唔識買，但原來全部係掩飾。<br />\n<br />\n一出手，就千里之外，直取皇帝首級，一劍封喉。<br />\n<br />\n論手段之狠毒，時機之準確，香港境內700萬人，真係只有望其項背。<br />\n<br />\n辛棄疾話：曹劉，生子當如孫仲策。<br />\n在下斗膽，加下一句：生女當如鄭月娥。<br />\n<br />\n大英祖國派此女中豪傑出手滅共，強呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n皇阿媽<br />\n事頭婆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3e62431de5cdee46a8d47b14ad817e34041868","tid":1217000,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"留芳百世<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bee8ea0acbc896cf29fd3f1a4c02a1bd5d55a05","tid":1217000,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:05:45.000Z","msg":"苦肉計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f3b054e7a1fbc68fac8247073e45eb3bb932ea","tid":1217000,"uid":11818,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:06:51.000Z","msg":"習帝：i am inevitable<br />\nCaptain trump captain eng都唔夠抽<br />\n林鄭： I am Lam Cheng<br />\nSsa........."},{"pid":"388c6ba56d7057615188176260670d14514845fa","tid":1217000,"uid":222646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"on9，佢真係蠢，唔係扮嫁"},{"pid":"8b432f815aa544560