" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5fcf065d1a70a2be39ea98fff6a2e1b6cb92e4","tid":1217000,"uid":67151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d050b2707d523922c074cee64409e2aeec9cf92","tid":1217000,"uid":21545,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"原來佢先係英國間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:40:56.000Z","msg":"咁我阿媽咪勾結外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4376c24302dfcea9ceae96bf59ca5959244d2a8b","tid":1217000,"uid":54959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:47:44.000Z","msg":"一壇送中，搞到韓國魚戇鳩失言，連中共扶植，民望高企嘅佢一下俾人反超，真係犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db1f3220ec25a98d3500e892cfa68fbdd01db28","tid":1217000,"uid":54337,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"遲唔搞，早唔搞，適逢美中貿易戰同台灣大選，先來搞送中條例。有無咁橋呀？<br />\n<br />\n時期準確到咁，不差分毫，命中目標，簡直係絕殺。手段非常高強。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2010728/org/0f1f009bdddaf003c746b4bc47a04e0c.jpg/wRmToIfrwGbSQlSD2THl1PxqueyOZLelUtI2lVLSNpU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2010728%2Forg%2F0f1f009bdddaf003c746b4bc47a04e0c.jpg%2FwRmToIfrwGbSQlSD2THl1PxqueyOZLelUtI2lVLSNpU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=583c4bd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n刁煬帝發夢都估唔到，港珠澳大橋開幕個日，行喺自己旁邊嘅個一隻粉紅老閪，連八達通都唔識用，廁紙都唔識買，原來係潛藏掩飾，最後關鍵時刻，佢一出手，竟然會害到自己雞毛鴨血，身敗名裂。<br />\n<br />\n黃蜂尾後針呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ed828f1d1ab728f678fcf967cb18c696313f7e","tid":1217000,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:37:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古有齊威王、越王勾踐、德川家康。<br />\n今有淋病月娥。<br />\n<br />\n平時庸碌無能，廢閪到核爆。<br />\n不飛則已，飛則一飛沖天。<br />\n不鳴則已，鳴則一鳴驚人。<br />\n<br />\n點估到一個師奶，連八達通都唔識用，廁紙都唔識買，但原來全部係掩飾。<br />\n<br />\n一出手，就千里之外，直取皇帝首級，一劍封喉。<br />\n<br />\n論手段之狠毒，時機之準確，香港境內700萬人，真係只有望其項背。<br />\n<br />\n辛棄疾話：曹劉，生子當如孫仲<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>謀</strong></span>。<br />\n在下斗膽，加下一句：生女當如鄭月娥。<br />\n<br />\n大英祖國派此女中豪傑出手滅共，強呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n皇阿媽<br />\n事頭婆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bdcfbfa126edac162ab61f39e5929fea7b32237d","tid":1217000,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecd17adb823c92caa41a5cbf9bdb6861310b75ae","tid":1217000,"uid":104109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d050b2707d523922c074cee64409e2aeec9cf92","tid":1217000,"uid":21545,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"原來佢先係英國間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />埋伏左20年嘅間諜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"德川家康，忍人不能忍之忍，成人不能成之成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c96a3ae74ae30ec0db18f5c4335f15051c0065","tid":1217000,"uid":25559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit